From 497a87bfb74e44e4449573582996a6dc4cc1c6b2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 22 Jul 2025 12:50:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Use scratchpad memory in rx path

Use scratch-pad memory in rx path in place of
rxcb area of skb for storing data. This will improve
performance in RX as the new contiguous memory will provide
better cache efficiency in rx path.

patch-dependency:
0400-0009-UPSTREAM-DP-Use-RX-HW-datastructures-in-rx-path.patch

Signed-off-by: Pavankumar Nandeshwar <pnandesh@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
